rows.label: qst001802_msg0001
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Bit weird to meet someone here!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]I've lost my Blade. I'm waitin' here
until she shows up.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0003
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Aw, what?!
Olua told you to come find me?

rows.label: qst001802_msg0004
rows.name: As you can see, I'm doin' just dandy!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0005
rows.name: But I don't wanna go back to Olua.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0006
rows.name:
She's always on at me like
"Train up! Get stronger!".
I've had enough of her naggin'!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Even just now, when I got knocked
into the Cloud Sea by a Moks Eluca!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0008
rows.name:
Sending you just proves it. She thinks
I can't get back on me own.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0009
rows.name:
She told me we had to go on a
training mission, so we've been
doin' some travelin'.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0010
rows.name:
But I hav'nae got any stronger,
not a bit. And Olua doesn't trust
me at all.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0011
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I don't wanna be a Driver any more!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0012
rows.name: We should say something to him.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0013
rows.name: Ask him if he can get back on his own

rows.label: qst001802_msg0014
rows.name: Tell him it's fine to be weak at his age

rows.label: qst001802_msg0015
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]...Uh...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0016
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Of course not!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0017
rows.name:
Ugh!
I guess I've gotta go back to Olua.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0018
rows.name:
UGHHH she's the WORST
BLADE EVER. I've got to give
her a piece of my mind!!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]I know I'm just a kid.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0020
rows.name: But...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0021
rows.name:
I wonder if I could get as strong
as youse if I tried really hard?

rows.label: qst001802_msg0022
rows.name: OK.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0023
rows.name:
I'll go back to Olua FOR NOW.
And I'll tell her not to be so annoying!
